Package org.TheGivingChild.Screens

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChildSprite
    ChildSprite controls the behavior for the children within the maze.
    MinigameRectangle
    Contains positional information where minigames can be triggered.
    ScreenAdapterManager
    The ScreenAdapterManager follows the Singleton pattern.
    ScreenCharacterCreator
    Screen for character creation.
    ScreenEditor
    This is the Editor Screen This allows user to place objects with attributes on a screen and then export the level with a correct XML file.
    ScreenHowToPlay
    This class creates the how to play screen.
    ScreenLevel
    Takes a given Level and allows the user to play it.
    ScreenLevelPackets
    No longer used.
    ScreenMain
    This class creates the main screen that is first seen when the game is started.
    ScreenMaze
    Maze screen that the user will navigate around.
    ScreenOptions
    This is the options screen.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ScreenAdapterEnums
    Enumerations to return ScreenAdapters for the ScreenAdapterManager The first few enums will be what the main_screen draws buttons for.
